es the feature and an array of step definition functions. Each step definition f
unction should be of the form `(options) => { ... }` where options contains `giv
en`, `when`, `then`. So `commonSteps` being `module.exports = ({ given, when, th
en }) => { ... }` is exactly the right format. This should work.\n\nLet me think
